Icon Font - Additional Set

Icons can come in handy when you want enhance the visual aspect of your application or just simply use a visual instead of plain text. In order for users to recognize an icon's meaning, the meaning must be universal. To keep all mercer sites and applications consistent, we've listed the different Mercer icons used according their respective functions.

Want to use an icon not found here? You can work with a Visual Designer to create a new icon that aligns to the Mercer brand and adheres to our visual standards. Contact Jeff Tudor for more information.
